{"tid":1661704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［解釋］交通津貼加碼原因","createTime":"2019-10-18T09:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T05:06:34.000Z","uid":255150,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"156b166399ab1e1ec41e90a29870700f85a68b1c","tid":1661704,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n特首林鄭月娥於《施政報告》中宣布，將公共交通費用補貼計劃加碼。市民每月交通費超過400元後，每1元車費由現時可獲0.25元補貼增加至0.3元，補貼金額上限亦由300元增至400元。在新安排下，若要「賺盡」400元津貼，每月車費料逾1,700元<br />\n<br />\n由7月起 已經好多人跳閘 用廢老卡<br />\n咁政府都係地鐵大股東 <br />\n而用廢老卡又係要政府補貼<br />\n政府發覺呢幾個月地鐵收入大幅減少<br />\n咁就將個交通津貼加碼<br />\n希望你班港豬唔好跳 唔好用廢老卡<br />\n政府變相咪多返收入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n大家千奇唔好用廢老卡/跳閘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616f833c494f191e519c870a15d7c447dbaecfaf","tid":1661704,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"政府開始驚驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918112d8949fd0e705404742a3d750601152f555","tid":1661704,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"益班水貨狗者"},{"pid":"4348a091feac565106197d82ccfbf26bc402bdb1","tid":1661704,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"918112d8949fd0e705404742a3d750601152f555","tid":1661704,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"益班水貨狗者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"果班拎正牌用都冇人捉<br />\n好多水貨狗都係用廢老卡"},{"pid":"770bd611d62decf6123503a5401645bd5cf86daa","tid":1661704,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7b3265ea3e8de9b229126bb31da9853f1f80fd","tid":1661704,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"廢老卡俾盡你返工出去玩一個月都用唔到兩舊水<img src=\"/assets/f